title: Overview: Bose QC35 Series II
description:
In this video we take a closer look at the Bose QC35 Series II.  This is the follow up to one of the best noise cancelling headphones out there and Bose has added Google Assistant compatibility with the touch of a button.  For more information on these headphones or to place an order please call us at 800-860-3736 or visit us at Abt.com.
